data.description: Welcome to your move in ready dream home! This stunning 2-story residence is nestled on a cul-de-sac, offering the perfect blend of space, comfort, and convenience. With 5 spacious bedrooms and 3 1/2 bathrooms, this home provides ample room for your family and guests. Step inside and you'll be greeted by an inviting living space, complete with an open floor plan and abundant natural light. The well-appointed kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring modern appliances and plenty of counter space for meal preparation. One of the highlights of this property is the expansive yard, providing endless opportunities for outdoor recreation, gardening, or simply relaxing in the serene setting. This home's central location is a commuter's dream, conveniently situated near Beltway 8, Hwy 45, and Hwy 288, ensuring quick and easy access to your daily commute needs. Schools, shopping centers, and hospitals are just moments away, ensuring that all your needs are within easy reach.
